ison, there's me shouting from the mountaintop... Why did I yell 'yay'...? There had to be something better I could've said...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"I-I think that was good the way it was!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Mhm, I think it was very fitting for you, no? It felt very... normal!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"episode191-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Ungh~, that's not supportive~...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"sad02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"I hear this special has had some fairly high praise within the industry. I'm sure many more requests for roles will be coming in. Aya-chan, you guys... You all have to get used to being on TV.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"episode191-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"M-mhm! I'll do my best!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Speaking of, you were supposed to make a guest appearance on a game show, Maya-chan. Whatever happened to that?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"episode191-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"That's right. I actually received the official offer already...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Really?! Congratulations, Maya-san!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"episode191-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"But... I'm not sure if I want to do it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"What~?! Why not?! This is such a good chance for you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"If it was me, I would have told them 'yes,' right away~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"episode191-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"What are you worried about?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"episode191-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"I'm glad that everyone thinks I was so amazing during the special.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"But I'm also pretty sure that I was able to do everything I did because you all were there.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"So what I really want is for all of us to be on the game show, not just me by myself.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"But if you do some publicizing of Pastel＊Palettes on TV, then eventually, we'll all be able to make appearances on other shows as well, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"episode191-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Correct. Hina-chan is right.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"episode191-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"But I understand how you feel. If I was told I had to appear on TV by myself, I would be unsure too...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"episode191-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"What am I supposed to do...? Aya-san, what do you think?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Hmm... I want you to do it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"It really would be better for Pastel＊Palettes' popularity, huh...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"No, that's not the only reason why.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Huh...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"So, uhm... I actually think of Pastel＊Palettes as a unit created from a mix of different colors.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Maya-chan, you've also said we're a band made from different emotions smashing together, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"I'm sure we all think the same, that we're a combination of unique personalities bumping heads.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"I think that at the moment, you're trying to to find your own color from the blend we've created. Actually, I am as well.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"That's why I think being on TV now can be a good opportunity for you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Aya-san...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Maya-chan. I'm always here for you! Now you appear on that show and give it everything you've got!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"I know for sure that it will make you better off, and it'll make Pastel＊Palettes better off!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"... Maybe I sound a bit full of myself though. Ehehe...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"episode191-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"N-not at all!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode191-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"You were able to communicate what we were all thinking, Aya-san!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"episode191-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"I have also learned a lot from you all and your different colors.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"episode191-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"If you're able to make your own color clearer and brighter by appearing on this show...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"episode191-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"I believe as companions, we will be able to influence each other in ways that we couldn't before.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"episode191-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"I also learned a lot from bein